
- @body_class = 'homer'

#outer-background-container(data-default-background-img="#{ asset_path('bg1.jpg') }" style="background-image:url(#{ asset_path('bg1.jpg') });")

.background-image-overlay

/ Outer Container
#outer-container

  / Left Sidebar
  %section#left-sidebar
    .logo
      %a.link-scroll(href="#intro")
        = image_tag asset_path('logo-home.png'), alt: 'Upmit'

    / Menu Icon for smaller viewports
    #mobile-menu-icon.visible-xs{onclick: "toggle_main_menu();"}
      %i.fa.fa-th
    
    %ul#main-menu
      %li#menu-item-better.menu-item.scroll
        %a(href="#better") better you
      %li#menu-item-carousel.menu-item.scroll
        %a(href="#carousel") how it works
      %li#menu-item-feature.menu-item.scroll
        %a(href="#feature") features
      %li#menu-item-signin.menu-item.scroll
        %a(href="#signin") start now!

  %section#main-content.clearfix
    %article#intro.section-wrapper.clearfix(data-custom-background-img="#{ asset_path('bg1.jpg') }")
      .content-wrapper.clearfix
        .col.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-2.col-md-9.col-md-offset-1
          %section.feature-text
            %h1 Up + Commit
            %p.text
              Upmit pushes you to achieve your commitments,
              %br
              so you can
              %strong be the better you.
            %p.btns
              %a.link-scroll.btn.btn-outline-inverse.btn-lg(href='#better') Find out more
              %span or
              %a.signin(href="/signin") sign in


    %article#better.section-wrapper.clearfix(data-custom-background-img="#{ asset_path('bg3.jpg') }")
      .content-wrapper.clearfix
        .col.col-sm-10.col-sm-offset-2.col-md-9.col-md-offset-1
          %h1.section-title Be the Better You
          %p.feature-paragraph.text
            %img.lazy.pull-right(alt="Rocket Up" data-img-src="#{ asset_path('transp-image1s.png') }")
            Changing for the better is always hard. It starts easy with a resolution, but sticking to it is the painful part.
          
          %h4.text We are here to help you up.

          

    %article#carousel.section-wrapper.clearfix(data-custom-background-img="#{ asset_path('bg2.jpg') }")
      .content-wrapper.clearfix
        #features-carousel.carousel.slide.with-title-indicators.max-height(data-height-percent="60" data-ride="carousel")
          / Indicators - slide navigation
          %ol.carousel-indicators.title-indicators
            %li.active(data-slide-to="0" data-target="#features-carousel") Commit yourself
            %li(data-slide-to="1" data-target="#features-carousel") Make it real
            %li(data-slide-to="2" data-target="#features-carousel") Social check-in
            %li(data-slide-to="3" data-target="#features-carousel") Get money back
            
          / Wrapper for slides
          .carousel-inner
            / CAROUSEL SLIDE 1
            .item.active
              .carousel-text-content
                = image_tag asset_path('goal.png'), alt: 'Goal', class: 'icon'
                %h2.title Commit yourself
                %p.text
                  Wanna start a new habit? Or trying to get rid of an old one? Create a goal by telling us what you are committed to achieve, how often and
                  for how long.

                
            / CAROUSEL SLIDE 2
            .item
              .carousel-text-content
                %img.icon(alt="One Dollar" src="#{ asset_path('onedollar.png') }")
                %h2.title Make it real
                %p.text
                  For every day you committed to take the action, you have to make 
                  %strong one dollar deposit
                  upfront. Only by successfully checking in on that day, you can earn that dollar back.
                

            / CAROUSEL SLIDE 3
            .item
              .carousel-text-content
                %img.icon(alt="Social Check-in" src="#{ asset_path('transp-image7.png') }")
                %h2.title Social check-in
                %p.text
                  You will have to check in your commitments by posting on Twitter or Facebook. Your family and friends are
                  gonna to be the best support you need.
            
            
            / CAROUSEL SLIDE 4
            .item
              .carousel-text-content
                %img.icon(alt="Lorem Ipsum" src="#{ asset_path('transp-image7.png') }")
                %h2.title Get money back
                %p.text
                  When the goal is completed, the money you've earned back will be refunded. We will only charge for the commitments you missed.
                  


          / Controls
          %a.left.carousel-control(data-slide="prev" href="#features-carousel")
          %a.right.carousel-control(data-slide="next" href="#features-carousel")

    %article#feature.section-wrapper.clearfix(data-custom-background-img="#{ asset_path('bg5.jpg') }")
      .content-wrapper.clearfix
        .col-sm-11.col-md-10.pull-right
          %section.grid.row.clearfix.clearfix-for-2cols
            / grid item
            .grid-item.col-md-6
              .item-content.clearfix
                %i.icon.fa.fa-bell
                .text-content
                  %h4 Get reminded
                  %p.text We will send you a reminder every day if committed to action. Email or Twitter DM.

            .grid-item.col-md-6
              .item-content.clearfix
                %i.icon.fa.fa-usd
                .text-content
                  %h4 100% Free
                  %p.text Our service is 100% free. If you all checked in, you will have every dollar of your deposit back.

            .grid-item.col-md-6
              .item-content.clearfix
                %i.icon.fa.fa-paypal
                .text-content
                  %h4 Secure payment
                  %p.text Your payment and refund will be securely processed by Paypal.

            .grid-item.col-md-6
              .item-content.clearfix
                %i.icon.fa.fa-share-square-o
                .text-content
                  %h4 Simple chech-in
                  %p.text @upmit #(commitment's hash tag) #(another one) ...
                  %p.text You can add more text as well as attach a photo.

    %article#signin.section-wrapper.clearfix(data-custom-background-img="#{ asset_path('bg4.jpg') }")
      .content-wrapper.clearfix
        %h1.section-title Start Now!
        .btns
          = link_to image_tag(asset_path('twitter.png')) + 'Sign in with Twitter', user_omniauth_connect_path(:twitter), class: 'btn btn-primary'
          = link_to image_tag(asset_path('facebook.png')) + 'Sign in with Facebook', user_omniauth_connect_path(:facebook), class: 'btn btn-primary'



  / Footer
  %section#footer
    / Go to Top
    #go-to-top(onclick="scroll_to_top();")
      %i.icon.fa.fa-chevron-up.fa-lg
    %ul.social-icons
      %li
        %a(href="https://www.facebook.com/upmit" target="_blank" title="Facebook")
          = image_tag asset_path('facebook.png'), alt: 'Facebook'
      %li
        %a(href="https://twitter.com/upmit" target="_blank" title="Twitter")
          = image_tag asset_path('twitter.png'), alt: 'Twitter'
    / copyright text
    .footer-text-line © 2014 Upmit LLC
    
    / Modal
    / DO NOT MOVE, EDIT OR REMOVE - this is needed in order for popup content to be populated in it
    #common-modal.modal.fade(aria-hidden="true" role="dialog" tabindex="-1")
      .modal-dialog
        .modal-content
          %button.close(aria-hidden="true" data-dismiss="modal" type="button") ×
          .modal-body
